Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:03.53,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Ooh.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:06.53,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That was...\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:13.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That was really good!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:18.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I agree! You feel way more in sync than before!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.37,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:22.34,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,That’s the best we’ve done so far.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.34,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It was perfect!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:25.93,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Mmm…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:29.87,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We’re not quite perfect yet.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:32.50,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We’ve still got a long way to go.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:36.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That makes it sound like you’re doing poorly, though…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:40.18,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I wonder…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:43.93,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Did I do well?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:48.47,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You were really cool, Kozue-senpai!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:54.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You’ve really improved. \NHere, I recorded it, so you can check it for yourself.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:55.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.63,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…You might be right.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:05.20,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We’re doing good.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.30,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Let’s keep at it.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.08,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,There’s still more we can improve on.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:16.99,Kozue,,0,0,0,,True. We haven’t perfected the dance yet, so let’s thoroughly review that video later.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:18.33,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:22.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But I think we’ll be fine if we keep going at it like this.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:27.64,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Also, we still have to come up with choreography for Kaho-san and Murano-san.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:30.23,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Oh, about that!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.68,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We came up with some choreography for ourselves.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.16,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wanna see it?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.23,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Huh!? You two came up with your own?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
