Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:03.47,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,U-Um…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.53,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I worked hard too…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
