Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:42.82,NPC,,0,0,0,,Oh?\N{\fs45}[Kaho & Sayaka & Tsuzuri & Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:49.77,NPC,,0,0,0,,Calling second-year student Otomune Kozue. Otomune Kozue.\N{\fs45}[PA Announcement]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:53.26,NPC,,0,0,0,,Please report to the student council room. Announcement over.\N{\fs45}[PA Announcement]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.79,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…What did you do, Kozu?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.62,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You’re already assuming she did something wrong!?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.39,Kaho,,0,0,0,,No way! I’ll go and apologize with you!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:06.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I haven’t done anything wrong, and I will be going alone!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.42,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You’re all making way too big a fuss over me getting called to go somewhere.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.13,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I-I’ll go instead!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.43,Kozue,,0,0,0,,There’s no need.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:16.98,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’ll be fine.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.35,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri, could you watch over the practice for a moment?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:23.52,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Sure.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.87,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I wonder why they’re calling you.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.47,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I might have an idea.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.30,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I’ll tell you later.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.93,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,And we were just getting into this…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.28,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s not like she’ll be gone for the rest of the day!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:45.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Let’s just keep doing our best, so we don’t worry Otomune-senpai later.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.52,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:51.36,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Please take good care of me, Tsuzuri-senpai!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.36,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:58.28,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Why don’t we do some light exercises until Kozu comes back?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.91,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Good job, you two.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.95,Kaho,,0,0,0,,H-How was that…!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:14.88,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That was… everything we’ve got!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.04,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I was really impressed.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.62,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,The choreo you two came up with was really good.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:26.89,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Nice job coming up with it yourselves.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:30.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Haa… haa…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:35.08,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ehehe, we really did it, Sayaka-chan…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.18,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,U-Um…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.18,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What is it?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.73,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’m really happy, for real.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:51.62,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,When you said you’d do your best for Kozu and me, I didn’t think you’d actually work this hard.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.21,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s… just…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What brought these compliments on…?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.84,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I thought about it while I was watching you two.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.46,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I realized you’ve been working so hard.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:09.08,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m happy to hear it, but…!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.32,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:18.54,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What happened to doing light exercises until Otomune-senpai comes back…?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
