Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.11,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What happened here…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.70,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was so happy that I got too excited\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.68,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,The choreo they came up with was really good.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.24,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:43.93,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I would have liked to see it, but I don’t think these two are in any condition to perform right now…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.31,Kaho,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you very much…!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.90,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’m okay. I can still keep going…!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:04.69,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry… this is such a mess…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:11.08,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry about it. \NI’m glad to see that Tsuzuri’s very pleased.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.24,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You two didn’t do anything wrong.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.57,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:22.05,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I guess it’s my fault for getting called over.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.44,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! What happened there!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Kozue-senpai!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:30.17,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Oh. It’s… nothing to worry about.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.74,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What happened?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:34.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it’s nothing to worry about.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.73,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Are you not gonna tell us?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.66,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,C-Calm down, maybe she just doesn’t want to tell us?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:49.89,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was called over… because she made a mistake somewhere?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn’t…!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Again, it’s really nothing to worry about.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Hm, how do I put this…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
