Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:13.60,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,S-So basically, you were invited to transfer to another school!?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.20,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I was only invited to.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.33,Kaho,,0,0,0,,My life is over!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:25.60,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’m going to wither as a flower bud!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.67,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Didn’t I say that I was only invited to?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.14,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Don’t leave me!!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.69,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s okay!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:40.85,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Look, I’m not planning on leaving, so it’ll be okay.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So, um…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.70,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,We really don’t need to worry about it, then?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:53.08,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m very honored that they requested me in particular to perform as a school idol with them, but…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:57.33,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, I get the final say on whether to accept or refuse.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:02.50,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s why there’s no need to worry like this. It was just an invitation.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.08,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:12.52,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that why you had a feeling you knew what you were being called for?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:18.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,When I momentarily left the stall at the festival, a girl approached me and handed me a letter from her club.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:23.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling I was being called regarding that.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:28.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,S-So… are you leaving me, Kozue-senpai…?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:33.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,No, no. I’ll be right here.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.89,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Are you sure you’re okay with that?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.26,NPC,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H00A3DF&\4c&H327A95&}H{*\3c&H319BBC&\4c&H51777F&}u{*\3c&H629399&\4c&H707469&}h{*\3c&H928B76&\4c&H907153&}?{\3c&HC38353&\4c&HAF6E3D&}\N{\fs45}{\3c&H00A3DF&\4c&H327A95&}[{*\3c&H0DA1D6&\4c&H3A798F&}K{*\3c&H1A9FCC&\4c&H437889&}a{*\3c&H279DC3&\4c&H4B7883&}h{*\3c&H349ABA&\4c&H53777E&}o {*\3c&H4E96A7&\4c&H647572&}& {*\3c&H689294&\4c&H757466&}S{*\3c&H75908B&\4c&H7D7360&}a{*\3c&H828E82&\4c&H85725A&}y{*\3c&H8F8C78&\4c&H8E7154&}a{*\3c&H9C896F&\4c&H96704F&}k{*\3c&HA98766&\4c&H9E7049&}a{*\3c&HB6855C&\4c&HA76F43&}]{\3c&HC38353&\4c&HAF6E3D&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:41.73,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What… do you mean by that?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.38,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’ll ask again.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.08,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you’re okay with refusing?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.18,Kozue,,0,0,0,,H-Huh…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:54.76,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying… I should consider their offer?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.05,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Have you fully considered it?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.97,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I don’t even need to.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:04.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,There’s no way I would leave Hasunosora.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:07.57,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I know full well what it feels like for other members to leave the club.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:12.25,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I was the one who invited Kaho-san to join the club and formed the current iteration of Cerise Bouquet.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:18.10,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And more than anything, I decided that I would lead this club as its president.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.51,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And at this point, even if I were to leave this school and join a new one,\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:27.19,Kozue,,0,0,0,,there’s no guarantee I would take well to those new surroundings\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:31.79,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I don’t know if I would be proud to perform as a school idol for that school.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:37.19,Kozue,,0,0,0,,See? There was no reason for me to accept their offer from the very beginning.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Fine. Then let me ask this…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:47.59,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Between that school’s School Idol Club and ours, which is more famous?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:57.39,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Setting aside past accomplishments and strictly speaking about how things are currently, theirs is.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:02.03,Kozue,,0,0,0,,They regularly appear at nationals, and last year, they placed well…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:05.56,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This is their club.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,The girl in the middle is the one who invited me.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.43,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Oh, I’ve heard of these people before.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:17.82,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,They’re famous for how in unison their performances are, right?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:19.82,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Right.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.82,Kozue,,0,0,0,,To be frank, they’re quite amazing.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:26.12,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s what their School Idol Club is like.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Why do you ask?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:36.01,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,So if you want to win Love Live!, you should join that club, then.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.93,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri… What are you trying to say?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.25,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s almost like you {\i1}want{\i0} me to leave.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.71,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I don’t, but…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.86,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,H-H-H-Hang on a minute!!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:53.21,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s not like Tsuzuri-senpai wants you to leave!!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.09,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Saya…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:00.41,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Our practice was going really well just now!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:05.88,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,A-And I’m really looking forward to performing at my first school festival!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.75,Kaho,,0,0,0,,C-Come on, let’s practice…!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:12.79,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Alright.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.18,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Let’s go, then.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
